title: AnoSTEP- *Anopheles stephensi* sampling in 56 sites across Kenya

projects.title: AnoSTEP
projects.subtitle: Close-kin mark-recapture study of Anopheles mosquitoes in Lake Kanyaboli, Kenya
projects.description: AnoKin is a close-kin mark-recapture (CKMR) study investigating population dynamics  and structure of Anopheles mosquitoes in Lake Kanyaboli, Kenya through genetic analysis  of kinship between individual mosquitoes.
